[Weaving a Tale of Love]

3
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:34,140
[Episode 27]

4
00:01:35,100 --> 00:01:37,200
Liuli presented the golden needle.

5
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:40,600
She said it is a treasure that can trade for money to help cure illness,

6
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:44,200
but she couldn't wait to sell the golden needle.

7
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:47,900
And she already died.

8
00:01:49,700 --> 00:01:54,600
Life and death are fate. This is her fate.

9
00:01:57,200 --> 00:02:01,000
Buddist Master, in the remaining belongings of Liuli,

10
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:04,200
have you ever seen a secret sewing book?

11
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:08,200
I have never seen any secret book.

12
00:02:08,200 --> 00:02:11,000
Buddhist Master, please think again.

13
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:14,600
Maybe there is some secret book she has never told you about.

14
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:18,800
When Liuli came, she had no belongings.

15
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:23,200
If she hid a golden needle, I would not have known.

16
00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:26,200
If she had a book,

17
00:02:26,200 --> 00:02:30,000
how would I not know?

18
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:41,400
Buddhist monks don't lie.

19
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:44,400
It looks like you are speaking lies.

20
00:02:45,200 --> 00:02:49,600
No matter what, now that I have gotten the golden needle,

21
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:54,000
then I am actually Number One Needle in the World.

22
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:57,200
Such a happy event!

23
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:25,600
Liuli, don't do things out of anger. Calm down.

24
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:28,400
I promise I sent this golden needle out.

25
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:31,800
I will bring it back for sure and give it back to you.

26
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:34,000
You are not me.

27
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:37,600
You don't know how important this golden needle is to me.

28
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:41,700
My matters, please don't be involved again.

29
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:45,900
You are so angry, I am at fault.

30
00:03:45,900 --> 00:03:49,100
But the Bureau of Imperial Attire is a dangerous place. Attire Expert Zhuo is wicked.

31
00:03:49,100 --> 00:03:50,800
You have to protect yourself.

32
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:53,500
Otherwise, your mother's golden needle is sacrificed for nothing.

33
00:03:53,500 --> 00:03:55,300
As for me...

34
00:04:00,190 --> 00:04:02,470
I will protect you.

35
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:09,800
Congratulations Master for getting the golden needle.

36
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:13,300
You don't need to worry about Attire Expert An's descendant.

37
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:18,400
As long as I can't find the person who was worshipping at the Hall of Thinking Heart that night,

38
00:04:18,400 --> 00:04:21,000
I cannot be at ease.

39
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:26,500
This Xiao Douzi is still the most suspicious person.

40
00:04:28,100 --> 00:04:30,400
You have to watch her carefully.

41
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:31,400
Yes.

42
00:04:31,400 --> 00:04:32,900
Attire Expert Zhuo,

43
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:38,200
I have waited for you for a long time.

44
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,900
Why are you waiting for me?

45
00:04:39,900 --> 00:04:43,000
I came to get my badge back.

46
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:46,500
Your badge... why would it be in my hands?

47
00:04:47,200 --> 00:04:51,800
Attire Expert Zhuo, others don't say it,

48
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:54,200
but that day I broke the palace rules.

49
00:04:54,200 --> 00:04:58,100
I was paying respect to the dead at Hall of Thinking Heart and you coincidentally saw me.

50
00:04:58,100 --> 00:05:01,800
I was in a rush to leave, and in the midst, I lost my badge.

51
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,800
But when I returned to look for it,

52
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:06,000
this badge had already gone missing.

53
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:09,100
I was thinking you must have picked it up.

54
00:05:09,100 --> 00:05:13,200
This badge is important. Without it, it will be hard for me.

55
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:15,200
I really had no choice,

56
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:19,200
so I could only come and find you.

57
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:27,800
That day at the Hall of Thinking Heart,

58
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:30,800
it was you?

59
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:32,400
It was me.

60
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:34,900
Who are you paying respects to?

61
00:05:34,900 --> 00:05:37,700
Why ask when you already know?

62
00:05:37,700 --> 00:05:42,000
That day, it was Attire Expert An's death day.

63
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:50,800
I heard from Xiao Douzi that a fairy shared skills with her in her dreams.

64
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:54,600
And that fairy claims to have lived in Hall of Thinking Heart.

65
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:58,800
And this Hall of Thinking Heart often has ghosts lately.

66
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:01,700
I am really not at ease.

67
00:06:01,700 --> 00:06:05,000
So I thought that the fairy must be Attire Expert An.

68
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:08,000
So that day, I went to pay respects.

69
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:12,000
Who would have thought that you would catch me? So I could only evade you.

70
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:17,200
Since you know that in the palace it is a crime to pay respects,

71
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:20,500
it breaks the rules, then why did you still do it?

72
00:06:20,500 --> 00:06:23,800
Of course, it is because I have guilt in my heart.

73
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:26,800
Thanks to you.

74
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:29,000
Thanks to me?

75
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:34,200
The Courtyard of Misfortune has always respected the dead, no matter rich or poor.

76
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:37,600
They would help them carry out their death matters.

77
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:41,000
Yet only Attire Expert An's body

78
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:45,400
was burned by myself to ashes.

79
00:06:45,400 --> 00:06:47,400
She couldn't be buried.

80
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:50,700
Attire Expert Zhuo, 11 years ago,

81
00:06:50,700 --> 00:06:54,000
who was it that forced me to burn the body to ashes?

82
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:56,100
Did you forget?

83
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:02,800
That night, I didn't see your badge.

84
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:05,000
Look elsewhere.

85
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:07,300
Did you really not see it?

86
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:10,800
Attire Expert Zhuo,

87
00:07:11,900 --> 00:07:14,600
you have no use for that badge.

88
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:16,400
Why don't you return it to me?

89
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:18,000
I really haven't seen it.

90
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:20,800
You have also said that I have no use for it.

91
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:24,300
If I had seen it, I wouldn't need to keep it.

92
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:33,600
Thank you for your help.

93
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:36,000
Please persuade Xiao Douzi

94
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:40,900
for her to not be in danger because of that golden needle.

95
00:07:40,900 --> 00:07:43,000
Thank you, Qiniang.

96
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:12,000
Being in the palace was to avenge my mother.

97
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:14,600
But now, not only can I not take revenge for mother,

98
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:18,600
I even gave the golden needle to the enemy that killed Mother.

99
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:22,600
Why am I so useless? So mischievous?

100
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:29,080
Xiao Douzi.

101
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:37,400
Xiao Douzi, I know you must feel really bad right now.

102
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:41,400
Good thing Master doesn't suspect your relationship with Attire Expert An anymore.

103
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:46,800
In order to learn sewing skills from you, she won't cause harm to you for the time being.

104
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:49,800
Your foster father also asked me to persuade you.

105
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:52,600
He said that the golden needle is something not with you.

106
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:56,900
Don't be in danger because of a golden needle.

107
00:08:57,800 --> 00:08:59,400
Pei Xingjian.

108
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:03,600
Foster Father, Qiniang. They are the people I trust the most,

109
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:08,000
yet they all have kept it a secret from me, making me an unfilial person.

110
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:11,800
I am so useless. How can Mother forgive me?

111
00:09:13,430 --> 00:09:16,050
- Xiao Douzi.
- Qiniang.

112
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:18,400
I...

113
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:23,400
Actually, she understands everything we have said. She just can't accept it.

114
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:26,900
Let her be by herself.

115
00:10:42,300 --> 00:10:45,500
[Embroidered Splendor Blooming Flowers]

116
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:01,400
It's not the new year or festival time.

117
00:11:01,400 --> 00:11:05,500
Why have you caused such a big ruckus and called me?

118
00:11:05,500 --> 00:11:08,000
You even invited the portraits of Yellow Emperor, founder of clothmaking,

119
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:11,000
and Lei Zu, founder of weaving. (Lei Zu was Yellow Emperor's wife, the first person in ancient China to grow silkworms for weaving.)

120
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:16,200
Is it because you have gotten the golden needle yesterday?

121
00:11:17,800 --> 00:11:19,800
Replying to Attire Chief Lin.

122
00:11:19,800 --> 00:11:24,200
This golden needle is from my teacher.

123
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:27,200
It represents the title, "Number One Needle in the World".

124
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:29,800
The meaning is not ordinary.

125
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:34,400
I am Madam An's only disciple. I should receive this item.

126
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:38,300
After Master died, the golden needle was nowhere to be found.

127
00:11:38,300 --> 00:11:43,000
After 11 years, it has returned to its owner, in my hands.

128
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:47,400
This is my luck and the Bureau of Imperial Attire's happiness.

129
00:11:47,400 --> 00:11:52,400
This is why I'm holding a solemn ceremony to pay tribute to the golden needle today,

130
00:11:52,400 --> 00:11:54,400
To tell everyone in the Bureau of Imperial Attire.

131
00:11:54,400 --> 00:11:58,000
It's also... to announce to the world.

132
00:12:00,800 --> 00:12:04,940
Attire Chief Lin, please take your seat.

133
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:31,990
I'll introduce you to it. The ceremony today has three parts.

134
00:12:31,990 --> 00:12:35,560
In the first part, Attire Chief Lin and Attire Expert Zhuo

135
00:12:35,560 --> 00:12:39,890
will lead everyone to pay respects to our founding ancestors, Yellow Emperor and Lei Zu.

136
00:12:39,890 --> 00:12:44,310
In the second part, Attire Expert Zhuo will lead everyone to pay respects to the golden needle.

137
00:12:44,310 --> 00:12:47,210
In the third part, everyone in the Bureau of Imperial Attire

138
00:12:47,210 --> 00:12:51,260
will pay respects to the new Number One Needle in the Wolrd, Attire Expert Zhuo.

139
00:12:51,260 --> 00:12:53,340
Wait!

140
00:12:53,340 --> 00:12:56,110
Is she stupid?

141
00:12:56,960 --> 00:13:01,040
Based on what I know, years ago when His Majesty bestowed the golden needle to Attire Expert An,

142
00:13:01,040 --> 00:13:04,120
and also bestowed her the title of Number One Needle in the World,

143
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:07,380
it was because Attire Expert An's dressmaking technique had attained perfection.

144
00:13:07,380 --> 00:13:11,130
In other words, it doesn't mean whoever obtains Attire Expert An's golden needle

145
00:13:11,130 --> 00:13:13,230
can call herself the Number One Needle in the World.

146
00:13:13,230 --> 00:13:16,140
The title of Number One Needle in the World should belong to the most capable

147
00:13:16,140 --> 00:13:18,510
and most talented person.

148
00:13:19,160 --> 00:13:23,590
Xiao Douzi, you are but a lowly sanitation medical officer,

149
00:13:23,590 --> 00:13:26,780
and are temporarily loaned from the Courtyard of Misfortune to the Bureau of Imperial Attire.

150
00:13:26,780 --> 00:13:28,350
You've only been here a short time,

151
00:13:28,350 --> 00:13:32,160
but you dare to spew nonsense here. Are you tired of living?

152
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:37,620
What I'm saying is probably what everyone in the Bureau of Imperial Attire is secretly wondering.

153
00:13:37,620 --> 00:13:42,090
I'm just more candid and speaking up about what I'm thinking.

154
00:13:42,910 --> 00:13:47,700
I am Madam An's only disciple and have focused on dressmaking for over 20 years.

155
00:13:47,700 --> 00:13:51,050
If I call myself Number Two in the Bureau of Imperial Attire, no one will dare to call herself Number One.

156
00:13:51,050 --> 00:13:53,080
Who dares to secretly disagree?

157
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:56,330
Don't talk anymore. Hurry and apologize to Attire Expert Zhuo.

158
00:13:56,330 --> 00:13:59,010
If you can't hold it for now, then you may ruin your ultimate plan. Please think clearly.

159
00:13:59,010 --> 00:14:03,540
Attire Expert Zhuo, you call yourself Attire Expert An's only disciple,

160
00:14:03,540 --> 00:14:05,660
but everyone in the Bureau of Imperial Attire knows

161
00:14:05,660 --> 00:14:08,710
that Attire Expert An didn't teach everything she knew to you.

162
00:14:08,710 --> 00:14:11,270
Since you claim to be the number one in the Bureau of Imperial Attire,

163
00:14:11,270 --> 00:14:13,610
do you dare to compete with me?

164
00:14:14,580 --> 00:14:16,850
Xiao Douzi, are you crazy?

165
00:14:16,850 --> 00:14:20,240
You rely on some cleverness, read some books, and learned some simple skills.

166
00:14:20,240 --> 00:14:22,960
You dare to boast nonsense in front of me!

167
00:14:22,960 --> 00:14:25,660
Guards! Drag her out and lock her up!

168
00:14:25,660 --> 00:14:29,940
Once the needle tribute ceremony is over, I will deal with her.

169
00:14:29,940 --> 00:14:33,020
Teacher, it's a celebratory event that you obtained the golden needle.

170
00:14:33,020 --> 00:14:35,350
It's also a great day today to pay respects to the golden needle.

171
00:14:35,350 --> 00:14:37,850
Let's not ruin your good mood because of Xiao Douzi.

172
00:14:37,850 --> 00:14:41,170
Please consider that he is young and ignorant. Just forgive him this time then.

173
00:14:41,170 --> 00:14:43,830
Xiao Douzi, hurry and admit you were wrong to Attire Expert Zhuo.

174
00:14:43,830 --> 00:14:45,610
How did I speak anything wrong?

175
00:14:45,610 --> 00:14:48,360
Attire Expert An didn't teach you her unique skills in dressmaking.

176
00:14:48,360 --> 00:14:50,530
She also didn't personally pass on the golden needle to you.

177
00:14:50,530 --> 00:14:53,670
How can Attire Expert Zhuo inherit the title of Number One Needle in the World?

178
00:14:53,670 --> 00:14:57,020
If you want to be proper and convincing to everyone in the Bureau of Imperial Attire,

179
00:14:57,020 --> 00:15:00,070
please accept my challenge. If you win,

180
00:15:00,070 --> 00:15:03,200
I, Xiao Douzi, will accept you as Number One Needle in the World.

181
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:07,090
Attire Expert Zhuo, you said so yourself that you've focused on dressmaking for over 20 years.

182
00:15:07,090 --> 00:15:09,560
I am, however, not even 20 years of age.

183
00:15:09,560 --> 00:15:13,050
I was only a lowly sanitation medical officer at the Courtyard of Misfortune.

184
00:15:13,050 --> 00:15:16,880
You don't dare to accept my challenge. Could it be that you are afraid of this lowly medical officer?

185
00:15:16,880 --> 00:15:19,600
Are you afraid of me, a junior who never learned formal dressmaking?

186
00:15:19,600 --> 00:15:23,250
I don't want to listen to your nonsense. Why are you all standing dazed?

187
00:15:23,250 --> 00:15:27,160
Hurry and drag out this insubordinate crazy person!

188
00:15:27,160 --> 00:15:28,830
Wait!

189
00:15:35,130 --> 00:15:38,230
Attire Chief Lin, you are the chief of the Bureau of Imperial Attire.

190
00:15:38,230 --> 00:15:40,610
I hope that you will speak a word of justice.

191
00:15:40,610 --> 00:15:45,670
If Attire Chief Lin also thinks that the bestowed golden needle and the title of Number One Needle in the World can be given out like playthings,

192
00:15:45,670 --> 00:15:47,790
I won't say anything then.

193
00:15:47,790 --> 00:15:50,870
I'm only afraid that once His Majesty hears about this,

194
00:15:50,870 --> 00:15:55,260
His Majesty will accuse Attire Chief Lin of incapable management as well as cronyism.

195
00:15:55,970 --> 00:16:00,390
Xiao Douzi has the Crown Prince and Talented Lady Wu behind her.

196
00:16:00,390 --> 00:16:04,620
Is he saying this to threaten me?

197
00:16:08,490 --> 00:16:14,360
Attire Expert Zhuo, Xiao Douzi should be punished for her rude words and insubordinate demeanor.

198
00:16:14,360 --> 00:16:18,960
However, he is publicly challenging your dressmaking skills.

199
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:23,600
If you drag him out to punishment, it would actually lead to gossip.

200
00:16:23,600 --> 00:16:26,930
Even if you have proclaimed yourself to be Number One Needle in the World,

201
00:16:26,930 --> 00:16:31,030
people will say you didn't get it properly later on.

202
00:16:31,730 --> 00:16:35,120
How about we wait until after Attire Expert Zhuo wins the challenge,

203
00:16:35,120 --> 00:16:37,620
then we will punish Xiao Douzi for both charges.

204
00:16:37,620 --> 00:16:40,460
Thereafter, Xiao Douzi can't speak up again,

205
00:16:40,460 --> 00:16:45,920
and everyone in the Bureau of Imperial Attire will be convinced. I can also report everything to the Directorate of Eunuchs

206
00:16:45,920 --> 00:16:51,490
to officially award you with the title of Number One Needle in the World.

207
00:16:51,490 --> 00:16:53,980
Wouldn't this be a perfect way?

208
00:16:53,980 --> 00:16:57,670
Attire Chief Lin is indeed a thoughtful planner and good manager.

209
00:16:57,670 --> 00:17:01,000
If I lose the challenge, I'm willing to accept punishment for two charges

210
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:03,430
and be accountable to everyone.

211
00:17:03,430 --> 00:17:08,500
I announce that the tribute ceremony will temporarily be suspended.

212
00:17:08,500 --> 00:17:11,500
Who gets the golden needle and who receives the title of Number One Needle in the world

213
00:17:11,500 --> 00:17:15,160
will be fairly decided through competition.

214
00:17:15,160 --> 00:17:20,000
Xiao Douzi dares to challenge Attire Expert Zhuo. Her spirit should be commended.

215
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:24,640
The competition will motivate everyone in the Bureau of Imperial Attire to learn from one another.

216
00:17:24,640 --> 00:17:27,940
Improving everyone's skills

217
00:17:27,940 --> 00:17:30,870
is originally why I transferred Xiao Douzi

218
00:17:30,870 --> 00:17:34,290
from the Courtyard of Misfortune to the Bureau of Imperial Attire.

219
00:17:47,320 --> 00:17:49,640
Xiao Douzi,

220
00:17:52,580 --> 00:17:56,500
why are you opposing me this way? Who gave you such boldness?

221
00:17:56,500 --> 00:18:00,120
People walk up, water flows down.

222
00:18:00,120 --> 00:18:02,960
Attire Expert Zhuo's dressmaking skill is clearly not as good as mine

223
00:18:02,960 --> 00:18:07,290
but you covet the seat of Number One Needle in the World. Why can't I then?

224
00:18:07,860 --> 00:18:11,760
Do you really think you can defeat me based on yourself?

225
00:18:11,760 --> 00:18:14,510
Why is Attire Expert Zhuo so angry?

226
00:18:14,510 --> 00:18:16,400
Didn't Attire Chief Lin say it?

227
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:20,180
We learn and improve from each other through competition.

228
00:18:20,180 --> 00:18:25,530
Isn't this your original intent to ask Attire Chief Lin to transfer me from the Courtyard of Misfortune to the Bureau of Imperial Attire?

229
00:18:25,530 --> 00:18:28,300
Don't keep sweet talking!

230
00:18:28,300 --> 00:18:33,720
Dressmaking depends on the hands, not the mouth.

231
00:18:34,550 --> 00:18:38,560
I will let you lose in a very embarrassing way.

232
00:18:39,290 --> 00:18:43,830
Then, Attire Expert Zhuo, please use your best skills

233
00:18:43,830 --> 00:18:46,500
so that I can be impressed.

234
00:18:53,970 --> 00:18:55,650
Imperial Guard Leader.

235
00:19:03,330 --> 00:19:05,170
Has something happened with Xiao Douzi?

236
00:19:05,170 --> 00:19:08,390
In front of Attire Chief Lin and everyone in the Bureau of Imperial Attire, Xiao Douzi

237
00:19:08,390 --> 00:19:11,460
openly challenged my master, saying only the person with the best dressmaking skills

238
00:19:11,460 --> 00:19:14,920
will be worthy of getting the golden needle and the title of Number One Needle in the World.

239
00:19:14,920 --> 00:19:17,970
As a subordinate who offends his superior, if Xiao Douzi loses the competition,

240
00:19:17,970 --> 00:19:20,470
he will be punished for two crimes.

241
00:19:20,470 --> 00:19:22,670
Did Attire Chief Lin allow it?

242
00:19:23,980 --> 00:19:27,600
Attire Chief Lin has reported to the Directorate of Eunuchs, and Director Gao is paying high attention.

243
00:19:27,600 --> 00:19:30,430
He said that this competition can not only motivate everyone to be more energetic,

244
00:19:30,430 --> 00:19:32,740
but it can also improve the dressmaking skills in the Bureau of Imperial Attire

245
00:19:32,740 --> 00:19:35,590
and set a good example to all the departments in the inner palace.

246
00:19:35,590 --> 00:19:37,710
The competition is set for three days from now.

247
00:19:37,710 --> 00:19:41,890
It has three rounds, including skills in dyeing, embroidery, and craftsmanship.

248
00:19:41,890 --> 00:19:43,660
Whoever wins two of the three rounds is the winner.

249
00:19:43,660 --> 00:19:47,430
Several of the grand consorts in the inner palace will be the judges.

250
00:19:47,430 --> 00:19:51,920
The winner will obtain the golden needle and the title of Number One Needle in the World.

251
00:19:51,920 --> 00:19:54,870
Xiao Douzi has made a risky move,

252
00:19:54,870 --> 00:19:59,100
but it is the best method to retrieve the golden needle quickly.

253
00:20:01,160 --> 00:20:04,700
By comparing the skills, of course, Xiao Douzi should win.

254
00:20:04,700 --> 00:20:09,520
I'm just worried that my master will come up with some fierce tricks.

255
00:20:10,640 --> 00:20:15,020
I can't wield any influence in the Bureau of Imperial Attire.

256
00:20:15,020 --> 00:20:18,040
I would still need you to help from the inside.

257
00:20:18,040 --> 00:20:22,030
The golden needle and the title of Number One Needle in the World are secondary in importance.

258
00:20:22,030 --> 00:20:24,730
The most important is Xiao Douzi's safety.

259
00:20:24,730 --> 00:20:30,090
If Xiao Douzi runs into any dangers, please come find me immediately.

260
00:20:57,290 --> 00:20:58,940
I've tried several times.

261
00:20:58,940 --> 00:21:02,000
Why can't I successfully dye it in the red shade in the rosy dawn?

262
00:21:02,000 --> 00:21:07,160
This fabric looks dull. It doesn't even look as good as the result from an ordinary dye house.

263
00:21:08,370 --> 00:21:11,220
Have I made a mistake in one of the steps?

264
00:21:20,730 --> 00:21:24,560
To dye the red fabric, the ingredients are usually Rubia cordifolia,

265
00:21:24,560 --> 00:21:28,290
red flower, ocher, and Laccifer Lacca.

266
00:21:28,290 --> 00:21:30,400
There is nothing wrong with my dyeing process, either.

267
00:21:30,400 --> 00:21:34,500
All the dyes are distributed by the Directorate of Eunuchs.

268
00:21:34,500 --> 00:21:37,400
So what is the problem?

269
00:21:43,470 --> 00:21:48,470
[Embroidered Splendor Blooming Flowers]

270
00:21:48,470 --> 00:21:50,830
What is happening with Xiao Douzi?

271
00:21:50,830 --> 00:21:53,230
Xiao Douzi has been testing her formula day and night.

272
00:21:53,230 --> 00:21:55,500
But the dyed fabric has been dull in the coloring.

273
00:21:55,500 --> 00:21:58,460
He has been very bothered by it.

274
00:22:01,320 --> 00:22:05,000
A kid who still stinks of mother's milk. How dare he challenge me?

275
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:07,440
He is still green.

276
00:22:07,440 --> 00:22:09,610
He overestimates himself.

277
00:22:11,510 --> 00:22:14,280
Master, the competition starts the day after tomorrow.

278
00:22:14,280 --> 00:22:16,830
Why aren't you making any preparation yet?

279
00:22:16,830 --> 00:22:22,360
The timing is just right. There is time to start the preparation now.

280
00:22:26,990 --> 00:22:29,540
I will get some ingredients for you from the Directorate of Eunuchs then.

281
00:22:29,540 --> 00:22:31,330
Go on.

282
00:22:34,890 --> 00:22:37,200
Master, what ingredients do you still need?

283
00:22:37,200 --> 00:22:40,890
Just get a little of all the ingredients.

284
00:22:42,070 --> 00:22:43,830
Yes.

285
00:22:57,570 --> 00:23:01,450
This Laccifer Lacca clearly has gotten damp. Take a closer look if you don't believe me.

286
00:23:01,450 --> 00:23:05,460
Using damp Laccifer Lacca to mix the dye, the colors will lose effect.

287
00:23:05,460 --> 00:23:08,740
That's why the red cloth I dyed is dull and not bright at all.

288
00:23:08,740 --> 00:23:12,660
What do you mean by that? You can't dye successfully, so you blame other people.

289
00:23:12,660 --> 00:23:16,490
Laccifer Lacca is the most precious ingredient among all the ingredients here.

290
00:23:16,490 --> 00:23:18,900
We have always stored it carefully.

291
00:23:18,900 --> 00:23:21,190
There have never been any problems.

292
00:23:21,190 --> 00:23:23,900
What? It is useless when you use it?

293
00:23:25,100 --> 00:23:30,200
Say... Either you have a problem in your procedure, or you haven't stored it correctly.

294
00:23:30,200 --> 00:23:32,000
It has nothing to do with us.

295
00:23:32,000 --> 00:23:35,600
Eunuch Yin, if you don't believe me, you can bring some more Laccifer Lacca from the storage.

296
00:23:35,600 --> 00:23:37,200
You'll see as soon as you compare them.

297
00:23:37,200 --> 00:23:41,000
Didn't you already receive all the last of the Laccifer Lacca in storage?

298
00:23:41,000 --> 00:23:44,800
Received it all? When will the new supply arrive then?

299
00:23:44,800 --> 00:23:47,200
At least 10 days even with the fastest speed.

300
00:23:47,200 --> 00:23:50,000
Ten days? How can that be?

301
00:23:50,000 --> 00:23:55,000
Without Laccifer Lacca, I won't be able to dye in red, and it's the best-looking red.

302
00:23:55,000 --> 00:23:59,200
I'm only in charge of the supply storage. I'm not in charge of your dyed fabrics.

303
00:23:59,200 --> 00:24:02,600
Please help me check then, lately who has received Laccifer Lacca?

304
00:24:02,600 --> 00:24:05,220
I will go ask for some to meet my urgent needs.

305
00:24:15,410 --> 00:24:18,310
Only you, there's been no one else.

306
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:21,400
That's not right.

307
00:24:21,400 --> 00:24:24,000
The box that I just saw in Master's room

308
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:27,800
should be containing Laccifer Lacca.

309
00:24:27,800 --> 00:24:31,670
Why does Eunuch Yin say that no one else has received it?

310
00:24:37,300 --> 00:24:39,000
Physician Dou.

311
00:24:47,800 --> 00:24:50,400
- Female Office Qiniang is here.
- Eunuch Yin.

312
00:24:50,400 --> 00:24:52,200
What are you picking up today?

313
00:24:52,200 --> 00:24:55,600
Attire Expert Zhuo wants to dye red fabrics, so she ordered me to pick up some

314
00:24:55,600 --> 00:24:58,400
red Rubia cordifolia, flower, ocher, and Laccifer Lacca.

315
00:24:58,400 --> 00:25:02,400
There is no more Laccifer Lacca, but there is plenty of the other ingredients.

316
00:25:02,400 --> 00:25:05,400
If the other ingredients are out, we can manage to think of other ways.

317
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:08,300
But, without Laccifer Lacca,

318
00:25:08,300 --> 00:25:11,900
Attire Expert Zhuo will scold me when she finds out.

319
00:25:15,800 --> 00:25:20,100
You can go back with ease. Your master won't scold you.

320
00:25:25,970 --> 00:25:28,030
Physician Dou!

321
00:25:32,000 --> 00:25:36,200
Physician Dou, don't be impatient. I know where you can get Laccifer Lacca.

322
00:25:36,200 --> 00:25:41,200
Sister Qiniang, are you thinking of stealing from Attire Expert Zhuo for me?

323
00:25:41,200 --> 00:25:43,000
How do you know that?

324
00:25:43,000 --> 00:25:45,200
Laccifer Lacca is a precious item.

325
00:25:45,200 --> 00:25:48,400
The storage room has always stored it properly, and there has never been any shortage.

326
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:52,500
With so many coincidences, it's naturally Zhuo Jinniang doing tricks.

327
00:25:52,500 --> 00:25:57,000
Sister, you don't need to take risks for me. Such a trivial matter won't be able to stop me.

328
00:26:07,400 --> 00:26:10,800
Xiao Douzi, why do you have time to come to the East Palace today?

329
00:26:10,800 --> 00:26:12,600
Greetings, Eunuch Wang.

330
00:26:12,600 --> 00:26:15,300
I came today because I'd like to plead to the crown prince for something.

331
00:26:15,300 --> 00:26:20,600
It's bad timing. His Majesty isn't feeling well, so His Highness is serving him in his sickbed.

332
00:26:22,830 --> 00:26:25,870
What do you need from Crown Prince? Just tell me.

333
00:26:26,600 --> 00:26:29,600
I came today because I'm hungry for snacks.

334
00:26:29,600 --> 00:26:31,800
I wanted to ask the crown prince for some berries to eat.

335
00:26:31,800 --> 00:26:34,200
This berry is precious, so I can't find it anywhere else.

336
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:37,000
But I've seen it a few times here at the crown prince's place.

337
00:26:37,000 --> 00:26:38,600
You... You...

338
00:26:38,600 --> 00:26:43,400
In this entire palace, you are probably the only one who dares to ask Crown Prince for berries to eat.

339
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:49,800
There are just berries, right? No need to wait for Crown Prince to return.

340
00:26:49,800 --> 00:26:51,100
I'll take care of it for you.

341
00:26:51,100 --> 00:26:53,400
Thank you very much, Eunuch Wang.

342
00:27:33,300 --> 00:27:35,000
Mother.

343
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:37,400
Liuli, what's wrong?

344
00:27:37,400 --> 00:27:40,800
Mother promised me to use the Impatiens balsamina flower to dye my nails.

345
00:27:40,800 --> 00:27:43,200
But the Impatiens balsamina flower has wilted.

346
00:27:43,200 --> 00:27:45,200
Mother, look.

347
00:27:50,400 --> 00:27:51,900
Come.

348
00:27:54,000 --> 00:27:55,600
Don't cry.

349
00:27:56,600 --> 00:27:58,600
It's all right that the Impatiens balsamina flower has wilted.

350
00:27:58,600 --> 00:28:00,800
Mother has plenty of solutions.

351
00:28:00,800 --> 00:28:04,700
But I love the color of the Impatiens balsamina flower the most.

352
00:28:05,400 --> 00:28:08,600
Yes, you'll have it.

353
00:28:36,300 --> 00:28:38,710
Mother, you are awesome.

354
00:28:38,710 --> 00:28:41,200
You didn't use even one petal of the Impatiens balsamina flower,

355
00:28:41,200 --> 00:28:45,800
but the color you mixed looks the same as the Impatiens balsamina flower.

356
00:28:45,800 --> 00:28:47,800
Among the tens of thousands of things in the word,

357
00:28:47,800 --> 00:28:50,000
every flower, bush, tree, fruit,

358
00:28:50,000 --> 00:28:52,200
has its own ingenius use.

359
00:28:52,200 --> 00:28:54,500
There isn't anyone or anything

360
00:28:54,500 --> 00:28:57,200
that can't be substituted.

361
00:28:58,200 --> 00:29:00,900
Liuli, when you run into problems in the future,

362
00:29:00,900 --> 00:29:03,200
just calm down and think it over.

363
00:29:03,200 --> 00:29:06,200
You'll be able to think of a solution as a replacement.

364
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:08,700
- Understand now?
- I understand now.

365
00:29:10,150 --> 00:29:11,660
Look.

366
00:29:13,000 --> 00:29:15,500
- Is it pretty?
- It's pretty.

367
00:29:19,400 --> 00:29:23,800
Mother, thank you for the wisdom that you've imparted.

368
00:29:23,800 --> 00:29:26,800
You've given me the courage to defeat difficulties.

369
00:29:26,800 --> 00:29:30,000
Your spirit in heaven must bless me

370
00:29:30,000 --> 00:29:35,000
to win this competition and retrieve your golden needle.

371
00:29:40,600 --> 00:29:43,000
[Bureau of Imperial Attire]

372
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:47,200
[Embroidered Splender Blooming Flowers]

373
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:52,200
Today is the first round of competition between Attire Expert Zhuo and Xiao Douzi.

374
00:29:52,200 --> 00:29:56,800
I especially invited two respected Grand Consorts as judges

375
00:29:56,800 --> 00:30:00,000
to show solemnity and impartiality.

376
00:30:02,000 --> 00:30:03,800
Attire Chief Lin,

377
00:30:03,800 --> 00:30:07,000
may I be bold to make an unreasonable request?

378
00:30:07,900 --> 00:30:09,800
Go ahead and say it.

379
00:30:09,800 --> 00:30:13,500
I suggest that our results will be shown in the competition

380
00:30:13,500 --> 00:30:16,400
without letting everyone know who did which one.

381
00:30:16,400 --> 00:30:21,000
This way, it will be the fairest way to judge without having a preconceived impression.

382
00:30:21,000 --> 00:30:25,800
It's not too late to announce the winner at the end of all the rounds.

383
00:30:25,800 --> 00:30:31,500
Xiao Douzi, are you doubting the two grand consorts' fairness? Against you,

384
00:30:31,500 --> 00:30:34,200
of course I will win.

385
00:30:34,200 --> 00:30:37,400
I wouldn't need the two grand consorts to favor me.

386
00:30:37,400 --> 00:30:40,600
I'm just afraid that Attire Expert Zhuo won't concede after losing

387
00:30:40,600 --> 00:30:44,600
and complain that the two grand consorts favor me.

388
00:30:46,440 --> 00:30:48,590
She is so clever.

389
00:30:48,600 --> 00:30:52,000
She isn't even afraid that she'll be too boastful and get embarrassed in the end.

390
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:54,400
We won't be biased at all.

391
00:30:54,400 --> 00:30:58,000
They will be judged by their true skills.

392
00:30:58,000 --> 00:31:02,400
Therefore, why don't we do as they say?

393
00:31:02,400 --> 00:31:04,400
First of all, it will be fair.

394
00:31:04,400 --> 00:31:07,700
Secondly, it will be more amusing.

395
00:31:50,200 --> 00:31:54,200
Your Highness, Talented Lady Wu just sent a messenger saying that His Majesty's high fever won't recede.

396
00:31:54,200 --> 00:31:57,800
He has been lying in bed since yesterday and can't get up.

397
00:32:01,170 --> 00:32:04,790
- Change my clothes.
- Yes.
- I'm going to the Hall of Immortal Nectar to see His Majesty.

398
00:32:07,400 --> 00:32:11,200
Oh yes, Your Highness. I heard that Xiao Douzi challenged Attire Expert Zhuo in public a few days ago.

399
00:32:11,200 --> 00:32:13,600
He wants to compete for the title of Number One Needle in the World against Attire Expert Zhuo.

400
00:32:13,600 --> 00:32:14,600
When did this happen?

401
00:32:14,600 --> 00:32:17,400
They are competing in the first round today. I heard that the winner is based on two out of three rounds.

402
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:20,800
A few days go, Xiao Douzi came to the East Palace to get some berries but didn't mention this matter.

403
00:32:20,800 --> 00:32:25,100
Probably-Probably he didn't want to let Your Highness get worried.

404
00:32:26,000 --> 00:32:27,600
Xiao Douzi is something.

405
00:32:27,600 --> 00:32:30,600
He has courage and insight.

406
00:32:30,600 --> 00:32:35,000
Transmit my message. Tell Xiao Douzi to compete with full force, and not hold back based on any concerns.

407
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:36,800
Zhuo Jinniang is the Bureau of Imperial Attire's Attire Expert.

408
00:32:36,800 --> 00:32:39,600
Even if he loses to her, it's not embarrassing.

409
00:32:39,600 --> 00:32:43,000
If he wins, I will uphold justice for him.

410
00:32:43,000 --> 00:32:45,200
Nobody can snatch away the title if he wins it.

411
00:32:45,200 --> 00:32:46,400
Yes.

412
00:32:46,400 --> 00:32:49,000
Eunuch Wang, you still need to accompany His Highness to the Hall of Immortal Nectar.

413
00:32:49,000 --> 00:32:52,000
Why don't I go for you then?

414
00:32:52,800 --> 00:32:53,800
All right.

415
00:32:53,800 --> 00:32:56,000
Thank you then.

416
00:33:21,000 --> 00:33:24,500
This is the first time I've seen such a luxuriant dyeing method.

417
00:33:24,500 --> 00:33:27,200
This red is like the ray of sunrise.

418
00:33:27,200 --> 00:33:31,000
The beautiful red even has a tinge of gold.

419
00:33:31,000 --> 00:33:33,900
The sun rises from the east, and it shines a bright path ahead.

420
00:33:33,900 --> 00:33:38,800
The fabric doesn't just have a pretty color, it's symbolism is very auspicious.

421
00:33:41,800 --> 00:33:43,500
Yun Hai,

422
00:33:46,000 --> 00:33:48,000
who won the competition today?

423
00:33:48,000 --> 00:33:51,600
I don't really know, but everyone is guessing that Attire Expert Zhuo won.

424
00:33:51,600 --> 00:33:55,600
Xiao Douzi is inside. Why don't you ask him yourself, Imperial Guard Leader?

425
00:34:14,800 --> 00:34:19,400
Xiao Douzi, you premeditated what just happened. Right?

426
00:34:41,890 --> 00:34:45,360
Attire Expert Zhuo, I can guess that I will win,

427
00:34:45,360 --> 00:34:48,670
but I couldn't guess that you would collude with the steward in charge of the supply storage

428
00:34:48,670 --> 00:34:51,110
to do tricks with my Laccifer Lacca.

429
00:34:51,110 --> 00:34:53,850
You want to use such a despicable method to win the competition.

430
00:34:53,850 --> 00:34:57,820
Attire Expert Zhuo, is this true?

431
00:34:57,820 --> 00:34:59,890
Xiao Douzi, don't speak nonsense.

432
00:34:59,890 --> 00:35:02,500
If you really used the damp Laccifer Lacca,

433
00:35:02,500 --> 00:35:04,380
how did you dye fabric with

434
00:35:04,380 --> 00:35:07,510
such a luxurious sunrise red color?

435
00:35:07,510 --> 00:35:09,950
Attire Expert Zhuo, you've confessed without being tortured.

436
00:35:09,950 --> 00:35:13,850
But thanks to Attire Expert Zhuo doing tricks with my Laccifer Lacca,

437
00:35:13,850 --> 00:35:15,340
otherwise, how would I have thought of

438
00:35:15,340 --> 00:35:18,840
using grape juice to replace the dye?

439
00:35:18,840 --> 00:35:20,630
Grape?

440
00:35:20,630 --> 00:35:23,620
You mean to say you used grapes?

441
00:35:24,990 --> 00:35:26,970
Ingenius!

442
00:35:26,970 --> 00:35:29,310
Truly ingenius.

443
00:35:29,310 --> 00:35:32,490
Blue-green comes from blue and surpasses blue.

444
00:35:33,970 --> 00:35:37,420
Attire Expert Zhou, just now, I saw the two grand consorts

445
00:35:37,420 --> 00:35:39,530
seem to really compliment you.

446
00:35:39,530 --> 00:35:41,830
They must have mistakenly thought

447
00:35:41,830 --> 00:35:45,450
that this sunrise red fabric came from your hands.

448
00:35:46,540 --> 00:35:49,910
You need to work harder in the next round.

449
00:35:50,670 --> 00:35:54,530
Two out of three wins, and you've already lost one.

450
00:35:54,530 --> 00:35:57,160
You can't afford to lose again.

451
00:36:07,850 --> 00:36:09,780
Xiao Douzi!

452
00:36:09,780 --> 00:36:11,560
You knew that you would win today,

453
00:36:11,560 --> 00:36:13,770
but you deliberately let everyone think that I am the one who won.

454
00:36:13,770 --> 00:36:16,830
You want me to become a laughingstock, do you?

455
00:36:19,170 --> 00:36:21,980
The higher you climb, the harder you fall.

456
00:36:21,980 --> 00:36:24,190
That's exactly the meaning.

457
00:36:25,990 --> 00:36:28,410
I want to lift Attire Expert Zhuo higher and higher,

458
00:36:28,410 --> 00:36:31,260
and then send you down the deep abyss.

459
00:36:32,390 --> 00:36:36,200
You want to win? Keep dreaming!

460
00:36:36,200 --> 00:36:39,030
I was temporarily careless today,

461
00:36:39,030 --> 00:36:43,220
that's why you got the chance.

462
00:36:45,190 --> 00:36:47,870
The topic for the next round is already announced.

463
00:36:47,870 --> 00:36:50,340
If Attire Expert Zhuo has the ability to hurt me,

464
00:36:50,340 --> 00:36:52,890
why don't you use it on dressmaking.

465
00:36:52,890 --> 00:36:56,030
Maybe you'll have a better chance at winning.

466
00:36:58,220 --> 00:37:01,640
[Embroidered Splender Blooming Flowers]

467
00:37:33,720 --> 00:37:35,830
I need to talk with you.

468
00:37:37,700 --> 00:37:39,470
Xiao Douzi.

469
00:37:40,110 --> 00:37:41,640
Hey!

470
00:37:42,460 --> 00:37:43,790
Just speak what you want to say here.

471
00:37:43,790 --> 00:37:46,780
Don't drag me around and entangle me.

472
00:37:46,780 --> 00:37:48,700
I heard everything you two said.

473
00:37:48,700 --> 00:37:52,780
Zhuo Jinning is sinister and cunning. She failed in the first scheme, and she'll definitely do it again.

474
00:37:52,780 --> 00:37:55,500
The crown prince has dispatched me to leave the palace in a few days on a mission.

475
00:37:55,500 --> 00:37:57,730
I won't be able to stay by your side to protect you.

476
00:37:57,730 --> 00:38:00,750
That's why I was worried and came over.

477
00:38:00,750 --> 00:38:03,030
Qiniang of the Bureau of Imperial Attire can help you.

478
00:38:03,030 --> 00:38:05,870
Don't get emotional and decline good will.

479
00:38:05,870 --> 00:38:07,550
Don't try to pretend to be a good person.

480
00:38:07,550 --> 00:38:11,520
If you didn't give the gold needle to Zhuo Jinniang, I wouldn't have needed to take this risk.

481
00:38:11,520 --> 00:38:13,670
