486
00:39:01,690 --> 00:39:04,070
Do you feel unwell anywhere?

487
00:39:07,590 --> 00:39:11,610
I only took a longer nap after noontime.

488
00:39:11,610 --> 00:39:15,100
Why are you so nervous?

489
00:39:20,710 --> 00:39:25,160
However, I feel so stuffy in the head after this nap.

490
00:39:25,910 --> 00:39:30,350
What time is it now? How long have I slept?

491
00:39:41,270 --> 00:39:43,470
Why isn't anyone replying to my questions?

492
00:39:43,470 --> 00:39:46,030
What time is it now?

493
00:39:51,140 --> 00:39:55,310
Replying to Your Majesty, it's still during the noon hours.

494
00:39:58,340 --> 00:40:01,040
I slept for an entire day?

495
00:40:01,040 --> 00:40:04,550
Your Majesty was unconscious for three days.

496
00:40:13,860 --> 00:40:17,580
I've always been drinking the medicinal soup from the Imperial Academy of Medicine.

497
00:40:17,580 --> 00:40:20,580
And I still haven't gotten better.

498
00:40:23,650 --> 00:40:25,640
Leave then.

499
00:40:28,170 --> 00:40:31,180
- A'Quan.
- Present.

500
00:40:32,470 --> 00:40:35,330
Last time, that Master of Pure Energy

501
00:40:35,330 --> 00:40:38,250
