502
00:40:38,250 --> 00:40:39,940
Why wasn't it used again?

503
00:40:39,940 --> 00:40:42,740
Replying to Your Majesty. The elixir is still being refined.

504
00:40:42,740 --> 00:40:44,890
I will go rush them now.

505
00:40:57,200 --> 00:40:59,060
Consort Yang.

506
00:41:03,750 --> 00:41:08,420
This time, His Majesty's illness is very different from the past.

507
00:41:08,420 --> 00:41:12,260
He actually wakes up less, but falls into a deep sleep more.

508
00:41:12,260 --> 00:41:15,320
Imperial Physician Zong, tell me the truth.

509
00:41:15,320 --> 00:41:18,410
How is His Majesty's illness?

510
00:41:18,410 --> 00:41:22,740
His Majesty's pulse is erratic and irregular.

511
00:41:22,740 --> 00:41:25,010
I don't have the patience to here your elaborate words.

512
00:41:25,010 --> 00:41:28,050
Just tell me if he can be cured this time.

513
00:41:28,790 --> 00:41:31,780
His Majesty's vital energy is weak. He's suffering from multiple

514
00:41:31,780 --> 00:41:35,350
organ failures. I'm afraid he doesn't have

515
00:41:36,530 --> 00:41:39,160
much more time.

516
00:41:44,250 --> 00:41:47,650
Remember, you must not mention this in front of anyone else.

517
00:41:47,650 --> 00:41:50,070
Yes, I understand.

518
00:41:50,070 --> 00:41:52,090
Leave then.

519
00:41:57,080 --> 00:42:01,480
Mother, there isn't much time left for us.

520
00:42:01,480 --> 00:42:03,630
It's not hard to topple Li Zhi,

521
00:42:03,630 --> 00:42:07,140
