522
00:42:07,140 --> 00:42:10,270
They keep ruining our good plans.

523
00:42:10,270 --> 00:42:13,080
Let's first get rid of Wu Meiniang.

524
00:42:13,080 --> 00:42:15,770
And then gid rid of Pei Xingjian.

525
00:42:17,210 --> 00:42:21,160
His Majesty has been relying on Wu Meiniang a lot lately,

526
00:42:21,160 --> 00:42:24,360
